Jo O'Meara https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo_O%27Meara 0 Joanne Valda O'Meara (born 29 April 1979) is an English singer and songwriter. She was member of pop group S Club 7 between 1999 and 2003. Her appearance on Celebrity Big Brother was cut short. O'Meara has been a member of spin-off group S Club 3 since 2008.
